      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations via benchmark problems. Required level 2 for MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Solver benchmarked against Taylor-Couette flow and lid-driven cavity problems. Numerical errors confirmed below 1% for relevant Reynolds number range. Required level met."
    },
