      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must be documented and match simulation boundary conditions within stated tolerances.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental conditions documented with flow rate uncertainty ±0.05 L/min and rotational speed uncertainty ±5 RPM. Boundary conditions in CFD set to match experimental means. Required level met."
