    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, which is acceptable under ASME V&V 40 at Model Risk Level 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision that the Class II CPB device hemolysis performance is acceptable relative to the predicate device, with RH < 1 confirmed across all five operating points.",
